istatus remains `Bad`, try rebooting the Access Gateway or check the		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
iDNS on the Access Gateway to ensure `magma.test` (or your domain)		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
ipoints to the core network.		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
